nodes.text: Sergio Paez is a storyboard and previsualization artist for Star Wars: The Clone Wars, a CGI-based television series that debuted October 3, 2008 on Cartoon Network as a continuation of the film with the same name, released two months prior. Paez also co-directed Star Wars Rebels Season Two episodes "The Lost Commanders" and "Wings of the Master" with Dave Filoni. He later directed The Triple Dark, the third episode of the first season for the Star Wars Resistance TV series, as well as Station Theta Black, the eleventh episode of the series.
